---
layout: base.njk
title: Blog - Commerce On Tap
description: Insights on e-commerce, Shopify, wholesale operations, and small business systems.
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Blog</h1>
    <p>Thoughts on e-commerce, Shopify, wholesale/B2B operations, and building better systems for growing brands.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="content-section section">
  <div class="container">
    {% if collections.posts.length > 0 %}
      <div class="blog-grid">
        {% for post in collections.posts %}
          <article class="blog-card">
            <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
            <div class="blog-meta">{{ post.date | dateDisplay }}</div>
            {% if post.data.excerpt %}
              <p class="blog-excerpt">{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
            {% endif %}
            <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="read-more">Read more â†’</a>
          </article>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    {% else %}
      <div class="about-content">
        <p>Blog posts coming soon! I'll be sharing insights on Shopify, e-commerce operations, B2B strategies, and more.</p>
      </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>
